ğŸ” Overview

Retail businesses frequently lose money due to poor inventory decisionsâ€”either stocking too little (leading to stockouts and lost sales) or stocking too much (leading to excess holding costs and wastage).

This project is an end-to-end data science system that:
	â€¢	Forecasts product demand using machine learning
	â€¢	Converts forecasts into actionable inventory recommendations
	â€¢	Estimates financial impact using inventory cost simulation
	â€¢	Provides a user-friendly web interface for non-technical users

The system is designed as a decision-support tool, not just a predictive model.

