ğŸ“Š Business Impact

Under simulated inventory cost assumptions, the ML-driven strategy achieved:

~62% reduction in inventory-related costs
compared to a naive baseline strategy.

This demonstrates how predictive models can translate into measurable operational impact, not just better metrics.

